        <h1>Sandwich Recipes</h1>
            
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#cucumber">Cucumber-Cheese Overload Sandwich</a></li>
                <li><a href="#spicy">Ultra-Spicy Sandwich</a></li>
                <li><a href="#common">Spice n' Cheese Sandwich</a></li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2 id="cucumber">Cucumber-Cheese Overload:-</h2>
            
                <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>3 Slices of bread
            
            <li>Chopped Cucumber
            
            <li>Melted Butter
            
            <li>Cheese Slices (2)
            
            <li>Salt
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Method:</h3>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Step 1: Take a slice of bread and spread butter on                 it.
            
            <li>Step 2: Add a slice of cheese on top of the bread                  slice with butter.
            
            <li>Step 3: Add cucumbers on top of the slice with                     cheese. 
            
            <li>Step 4: Cover that piece of bread with another                     slice of bread.
            
            <li>Step 5: Add a cheese slice on the second bread.
            
            <li>Step 6: Add salt and more cucumber slices on the                   second bread.
            
            <li>Step 7: Spread butter on the last slice of bread                   and use it to cover the second bread.
                
            </li>
        </ul>
    
    <h4>Your Cucumber-Cheese Overload sandwich is ready!</h4>
    
    <h5>For a mini version of the Cucumber-Cheese Overload                sandwich, use only two slices of bread.</h5>
    
    <h2 id="spicy">Ultra-Spicy Sandwich:-</h2>
        
        <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>3 Slices of bread
            
            <li>Chopped Cucumber
            
            <li>Chopped Tomato
            
            <li>Melted Butter
            
            <li>Black Pepper
            
            <li>Oregano (Optional)
            
            <li>Chilli Flakes
            
            <li>Spice Dip (Chutney)
            
            <li>Salt
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Method:</h3>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Step 1: Take a slice of bread and spread butter on                 it.<br>
            
            <li>Step 2: Add cucumbers on top of the slice with                     butter. 
            
            <li>Step 3: Add salt and black pepper on that slice.
            
            <li>Step 4: Cover that piece of bread with another                     slice of bread.
            
            <li>Step 5: Add some spice dip on the second bread.
            
            <li>Step 6: Add tomatoes on the second bread.
            
            <li>Step 7: Add oregano and/or chilli flakes on this                   bread.
            
            <li>Step 8: Add a mix of butter and spice dip on the                  last bread and use it to cover the second bread.
                
            </li>
        </ul>
    
    <h4>Your Ultra-Spicy Sandwich is ready!</h4>
    
    <h5>For a mini version of the Ultra-Spicy Sandwich, use only two slices of bread.</h5>
    
    <h2 id="common">Spice n' Cheese Sandwich:-</h2>
        
        <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>3 Slices of bread
            
            <li>Chopped Cucumber
            
            <li>Chopped Tomato
            
            <li>Melted Butter
            
            <li>Black Pepper
            
            <li>Oregano (Optional)
            
            <li>Chilli Flakes (Optional)
            
            <li>Cheese Slice
            
            <li>Salt
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Method:</h3>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Step 1: Take a slice of bread and spread butter on                 it.<br>
            
            <li>Step 2: Add cucumbers on top of the slice with                     butter. 
            
            <li>Step 3: Add salt and black pepper on that slice.
            
            <li>Step 4: Cover that piece of bread with another                     slice of bread.
            
            <li>Step 5: Add a cheese slice on the second bread.
            
            <li>Step 6: Add tomatoes on the second bread.
            
            <li>Step 7: Add oregano and/or chilli flakes on this                   bread.
            
            <li>Step 8: Add butter on the last bread and use it to                 cover the second bread.
                
            </li>
        </ul>
